HEADWORD: Rudmasday
<hw>Rud"mas*day</hw> <pr>(r⟦oomac⟧d"m⟦adot⟧s*d⟦amac⟧`)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Rood</er>, <er>Mass</er>,
